    entryTitle: The Forge of Eternal Flames
    category: Locations
    depthLevel: 3
    unlockCondition: 1
    unlockRequirement: 10
    unlockDescription: Play for 10 minutes
    description: 'Hidden in the Ironpeak Mountains, this forge burns with fires that
      never die. Legend says the flames were lit by dragons and blessed by gods.


      Ancient
      meteoric anvils and perfect-pitch hammers guide smiths in creating the most
      powerful runic weapons.'
    previewText: Mysterious knowledge awaits...
    icon: {fileID: 0}
    isUnlocked: 0
    readCount: 0
  - faction: 1
    entryTitle: The Corrupted
    category: Characters
    depthLevel: 1
    unlockCondition: 0
    unlockRequirement: 0
    unlockDescription: Available from start
    description: 'Once-mortal beings transformed by Void energy. Their flesh becomes
      crystalline and their eyes glow purple. They retain intelligence but gain terrible
      abilities.


      Many struggle with their lost humanity, caught between their
      former lives and dark nature.'
    previewText: Mysterious knowledge awaits...
    icon: {fileID: 0}
    isUnlocked: 1
    readCount: 0
  - faction: 1
    entryTitle: Void Crystals
    category: Technology
    depthLevel: 1
    unlockCondition: 0
    unlockRequirement: 0
    unlockDescription: Available from start
    description: 'Purple-black crystals that grow where Void influence is strongest.
      They pulse with malevolent energy and can corrupt living beings.


      The
      crystals seem collectively intelligent, growing in purposeful patterns that
      may be fragments of a greater Void consciousness.'
    previewText: Mysterious knowledge awaits...
    icon: {fileID: 0}
    isUnlocked: 1
    readCount: 0
  - faction: 1
    entryTitle: The Void Incursion
    category: History
    depthLevel: 2
    unlockCondition: 2
    unlockRequirement: 5
    unlockDescription: Serve 5 customers
    description: 'The catastrophic event that began the War of Shadows. Reality was
      torn open, allowing Void creatures and energy to pour into our world.


      The
      Incursion lasted only three days, but its effects ripple through history. Smaller
      rifts still appear randomly.'
    previewText: Mysterious knowledge awaits...
    icon: {fileID: 0}
    isUnlocked: 0
    readCount: 0
  - faction: 1
    entryTitle: Shadowlord Malachar
    category: Characters
    depthLevel: 2
    unlockCondition: 2
    unlockRequirement: 5
    unlockDescription: Serve 5 customers
    description: 'The first and most powerful Corrupted, once a noble king. His attempts
      to harness Void energy for defense transformed him into something beyond mortal
      comprehension.


      Now twelve feet tall with obsidian flesh, he seeks to
      ''elevate'' all life through Void corruption.'
    previewText: Mysterious knowledge awaits...
    icon: {fileID: 0}
    isUnlocked: 0
    readCount: 0
